# money-free Development Guidelines

Last updated: 2026-03-11

## Active Technologies
- TypeScript 5.x, Node.js 20.x (backend), Node.js 18+ (frontend) (004-stock-vcp-analysis)
- SQLite (已存在 VcpScanResult, KLineData, Stock 表) (004-stock-vcp-analysis)

### Backend
- **Node.js 20.x** (REQUIRED - see backend-environment.mdc)
- NestJS
- TypeScript 5.x
- Prisma ORM
- SQLite 3.40+ (单文件数据库，WAL模式，约2.6GB)

### Frontend
- Node.js 18+
- React 18
- TypeScript 5.x
- Vite
- Ant Design

## Project Structure

```text
money-free/
├── backend/          # NestJS backend
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── modules/  # Business modules (vcp, prisma, etc.)
│   │   ├── services/ # Business services
│   │   └── scripts/  # Data processing scripts
│   ├── prisma/       # Database schema
│   └── data/         # SQLite database
├── frontend/         # React frontend
│   └── src/
│       ├── components/
│       ├── pages/
│       └── services/
└── .cursor/
    └── rules/        # Development guidelines
```

## Important Commands

### Backend (Node 20 Required!)
```bash
cd backend
nvm use 20              # Switch to Node 20
npm run start:dev       # Start development server
./start-backend.sh      # Or use start script

# Database
npx prisma generate     # Generate Prisma Client
npx prisma db push      # Sync schema to database
npx prisma studio       # Open database GUI
```

### Frontend
```bash
cd frontend
npm run dev            # Start development server
```

## Code Style

- TypeScript strict mode enabled
- Follow ESLint and Prettier configurations
- Use functional components with hooks in React
- Use NestJS decorators and dependency injection in backend

